The Ismael Women Association in Kenya, in partnership with the Kenya Women and Children Wellness Centre, hosted top-notch women to a luncheon at the InterContinental Hotel. The event was meant to celebrate women across the globe. Guests present included politician Esther Passaris, Kenya Women Holding chief executive Jennifer Riria and former Vice President Moody Awori,among many others.Guests made a pledge to promote peace and unity during the elections, led by Wellness and Children's Centre president Deloris Jordan.